popularityCurve.label: guess what this is pretty fascinating i was going back to new york for a few weeks and a friend suggested i perform some ritual to thank the universe for my good luck so i brought my gold shoe along i got a piece of cardboard and wrote on it miracle shoe size 8 if this shoe fits you please take it it brought me good luck and now i want to pass it on to you whoever you are i don't know who got it i put it right next to a methadone clinic so maybe it's gone to someone who's really struggling when i left i was crying with joy at being able to pass it on
